short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Click2call integration of the Cely desktop application. Allows you to call the selected phone on the web page.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
With the CELY extension, Click2Call functionality enables calling telephone numbers on any webpage, just select the number, right click and press Click2call.
Our extension do not transorm the pages in any way
Please note that this extension can be used with CELY desktop application of any version.
